<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>REDEEMED</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tatsa ka hih genzak nuom ka sai,
 Belam No thisan a tatsa;
 Zahngaihna tawp neilo-in ei tan,
 A cha ka hi, kumsawt chanin.

[V2]
 Tatsa, tatsa,
 Belam No thisan a tatsa;
 Tatsa, tatsa,
 A cha ka hi, kumsawt chanin.

[V3]
 2. Tatsa, Isu-ah ka nun nuom hi,
 Nawpna, pakna, ka gen zo puoi;
 Ama'n kumsawt chanin ei umpih,
 A mun vak ah umzing ing ka.

[V4]
 3. Ei Tanpa nun nuom ka ngaihtuoh a,
 Sunni tumin ka ngaihtuoh hi;
 Thip mai thei ka hih tak loh ziekin,
 Kumkhuo'n hehpihna la'n ka sai.

[V5]
 4. Dan leh ka kipahna Lalpen chuh,
 Lopina mun achun mu'ng ka;
 Hehpihna'n ka kalsuon cheng A pu'i,
 Zan khawthim ale la ei piei.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>252</hymn_number>
</song>